| 🔴 Critical | 2 | `Underscore()` 4-alloc regex chain; `Pascalize()` 12+ allocs per call |
| 🟡 Moderate | 5 | `Camelize` slice, `InflectionRule` compiled regex & double-eval, `.ToLower()` culture, missing `GeneratedRegex` |
